  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators want to look at how patients admitted after passing out (syncope) or nearly
      passing out (pre-syncope) do after going home and how many of them remain free of symptoms of
      syncope or pre-syncope.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
